{"tid":1976610,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"防疫！Amabie娘！","createTime":"2020-04-17T10:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T14:59:59.000Z","uid":246648,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b7c0b319736fc38038c0cd8f414e311ff2c60e","tid":1976610,"uid":246648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:49:04.000Z","msg":"利申:無貼烏賊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCHCOw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCHCOw7.jpg&h=f8906c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/artworks/80851811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixiv.net%2Fartworks%2F80851811&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU9%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=755d65ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pixiv.net/artworks/80851811</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAmabie（日語：アマビエ）是一種源於日本傳說的人魚形生物。跟據傳說的敘述，它有三條腿，從海中出現，並且會保佑豐收，或者保佑人們不受疫病滋擾。 <br />\n<br />\n傳說中，Amabie曾於江戶時代弘化三年四月中旬（公元1846年5月中旬）出現在肥後國（今日本熊本縣）。每天晚上，人們都可以看到海上有一個發光物體。當地的官吏去海灘上查看，發現了「Amabie」。根據官吏繪製的草圖，這種怪物有長頭髮、嘴像鳥喙，從頸部以下都被鱗片覆蓋，並且長著三條腿。據官吏所說，怪物自稱為「Amabie」，住在海上，並預言說從今起往後的六年都會有好收成，如果疫病蔓延，只要把怪物的畫像給生病的人看，他們的病痛就會被治癒。話畢，Amabie就回到了海中。後來，這個故事和Amabie的畫像被一同雕刻在了木版上用於印刷，這使得Amabie的傳說得以在日本流傳開來。<br />\n<br />\n在2019冠狀病毒病流行時期，Amabie在日本的Twitter上成為了熱門話題。許多漫畫家（如羽海野千花、岡崎真里與青木俊直）都在社交網站上發布了以Amabie為主題的卡通形象作品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amabie\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAmabie&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU9%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=1703f0c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amabie</a>"},{"pid":"abbfb4972a13fad76a3c0917f9492c1ee3082359","tid":1976610,"uid":246648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jnJRTHn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjnJRTHn.jpg&h=15133954&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c446ee9380fb768c4852d015bfd6dea3826cf9a9","tid":1976610,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T13:29:03.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"30c6624839c4bd156e3a411702e1b6c0bbfc7dd8","tid":1976610,"uid":246648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:59:59.000Z","msg":"補返幾張Amabie<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/78/89/qJeZoKKalKCYq6Sg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F78%2F89%2FqJeZoKKalKCYq6Sg.jpg&h=50deaa04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/3jLA5pkLhJwpOne8lZyd8kC_eFNYMYrLruGRkvaUaq3bXu4udfFinrsAfl-QX_7GhxivHWHh1KYfjUThP5V9YU21HwQ5n-Xwj8_Oks4Lu_Z-jiPcads__A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2F3jLA5pkLhJwpOne8lZyd8kC_eFNYMYrLruGRkvaUaq3bXu4udfFinrsAfl-QX_7GhxivHWHh1KYfjUThP5V9YU21HwQ5n-Xwj8_Oks4Lu_Z-jiPcads__A&h=c7bcfbe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.atlasobscura.com/article_images/lg/73629/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.atlasobscura.com%2Farticle_images%2Flg%2F73629%2Fimage.jpg&h=09d95765&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}